{"tid":1647673,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【經典動畫再拍真人版】Camila將演灰姑娘 Billy化身黑人男仙子","createTime":"2019-10-12T00:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T11:16:00.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a10da976e0d725416ec6dd803b91efe4b0414962","tid":1647673,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:30:56.000Z","msg":"今年4月曾傳出消息指，古巴裔小天后 Camila Cabello將會於經典動畫《灰姑娘》真人版中飾演女主角，而最近就有指，剛憑《紐約萬花筒》（Pose）贏出艾美獎的黑人同志男星Billy Porter亦有份參演，更是飾演仙子教母一角。<br />\n<br />\n擁有魔法讓灰姑娘變靚靚的仙子教母原本是白人女性角色，但就有指電影公司將會起用Billy化身黑人男仙子。電影將會由女導演Kay Cannon執導，Camila Cabello亦會親自參與音樂部份。電影即將開拍，並會於2021年5月上映。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AzatYS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzatYS8.jpg&h=ac592112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191012/60142850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60142850&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=b8e10c32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191012%2F60142850&h=7aa962f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191012/60142850</a>"},{"pid":"2418e275d4ffe376681f1d859205b8a919457e70","tid":1647673,"uid":36072,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T00:32:46.000Z","msg":"叫做好過之前條黑人美人魚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b1f1b0c2b2a043c3cea23a0adce9231a32bb69","tid":1647673,"uid":10338,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:11:13.000Z","msg":"米奇d逆向歧視好嚴重下"},{"pid":"65d6449e8e08be1fafd5b32673170c5329a1d879","tid":1647673,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T01:12:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21752eb9cf0a4df